  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \n  \nRoot cause:  \nWeb worker listens to network state changes by adding observers to NetworkStateNotifier’s connection_observers_, which is a HashMap. When erasing an observer in connection_observers_ without acquiring lock will lead to heap use-after-free or heap buff"
